'''天马塚'''（{{kor|諺=천마총|漢=天馬塚|羅=Cheonmachong|f=y}}）位于[[大韩民国|大韩民国]][[庆尚北道|庆尚北道]][[庆州历史遗迹地区|庆州历史遗迹地区]]，天馬塚墓主身分尚未確認，一說為新羅第22代國王[[智證王|智證王]]（西元500－514年在位）。<ref name="Kipfer, p.232">Barbara Ann Kipfer, [http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN0306461587&id=XneTstDbcC0C&pg=PA232&lpg=PA232&dq=heavenly+horse+tomb&sig=q8Ex1URSTf1JeCCt99TZ0skQpPE ''Encyclopedic Dictionary of Archaeology'', p.232] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN0306461587&id=XneTstDbcC0C&pg=PA232&lpg=PA232&dq=heavenly+horse+tomb&sig=q8Ex1URSTf1JeCCt99TZ0skQpPE |date=20121106035324 }}</ref> 

天马塚是典型的[[新罗|新罗]]墓葬结构，棺木东西摆放，上方有大石头和泥土覆盖。<ref name="Nelson, p.250">Sarah Milledge Nelson, [http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN0521407834&id=sANORB_MSRUC&pg=PA250&lpg=PA250&q=heavenly+horse+tomb&vq=heavenly+horse+tomb&dq=heavenly+horse+tomb&sig=LTF-fBz3h8BKboUaHRRurys4ORg ''The Archaeology of Korea'', p.250] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN0521407834&id=sANORB_MSRUC&pg=PA250&lpg=PA250&q=heavenly+horse+tomb&vq=heavenly+horse+tomb&dq=heavenly+horse+tomb&sig=LTF-fBz3h8BKboUaHRRurys4ORg |date=20121106035335 }}</ref> 陵墓直径47米，周长157米，高12.7米。该墓有11500件文物出土，其中包括天马图。

